esting-data-for-wordpress-themes-and-plugins'' title=''WP Test is a site that any WordPress theme or plugin developer will want to bookmark. Created by WordPress developer Michael Novotny, WP Test exists to provide test data for WordPress themes and plugins. The site is very simple and includes only a download and a demo button. What’s in the download package? WP Test sums it up nicely: A fantastically exhaustiv [&hellip;]''>WPTavern: WP Test: Unit Testing Data for WordPress Themes and Plugins</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
